  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-lg-7">
      <p>Mattamy Homes and Solara Resort have partnered with WhiteWater West to bring an international competition level FlowRider system to Central Florida!</p>
      <h1>What is a FlowRider?</h1>
      <p>
        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="margin-right:1em;color:#96d2b6;"></i>This compact “wave-in-a-box” allows guests to try the thrill of surfing/wakeboarding in a controlled environment.
      </p>
      <p>
        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="margin-right:1em;color:#96d2b6;"></i>FlowRiding is ideal for participants of all ages and skill levels, including first time riders. Our pros have competed in national competitions and are happy to share their knowledge with every guest!
      </p>
      <p>
        <i class="fas fa-circle" style="margin-right:1em;color:#96d2b6;"></i>With a tensioned fabric ride surface, FlowRiding is about as safe as it gets for an extreme sport.
      </p>
    </div>
